constituent: limb, moon, month, flesh, part of the body, branch, ten, needle, crotch
koohiiStory1: The limbs that this kanji represents are parts of the body that are connected to the trunk, like the main branches to a tree (“arms and legs” is the second meaning of this kanji). In other words, limbs are "flesh branches".
koohiiStory2: Limbs are body parts that branch off.
myStory: chi. tay chân. bộ phận nhánh
